### Using the Intel HAXM

Using the Android emulator can be incredibly frustrating simply because it is so slow. If you are using an Intel architecture, you can take advantage of some Intel development tools to greatly decrease the time required to start and operate the emulator. This improves performance by an order of magnitude for me, so it is definitely worth the effort.  

Please visit the [Intel web site](http://software.intel.com/en-us/android/articles/speeding-up-the-android-emulator-on-intel-architecture) for additional information and detailed installation instructions for both Windows and Linux.
